{"build_type":"executable","description":"Naming-policy audit tool. Reads {\"roots\":[dir,...]} from stdin, enumerates every package under those roots into the universe (parsed ASTs), and reports every package_name and function name that fails the naming policy (>=5 hyphen-joined words, each >=5 lowercase letters or a registered allowlisted abbreviation). Emits {violations:[{kind,name}], violation_count, packages_scanned}. Non-gating: it only reports — this is the worklist for the rename track; the same name_satisfies_naming_policy lib becomes a fail-closed build gate once the tree complies. Reuses read_all_of_stdin, decode_entire_source_building_document, locate_named_member_inside_mapping, enumerate_universe_packages, naming_abbreviation_allowlist_json, begin_empty_sequence_document_value, count_members_inside_container_value, scan_each_package_for_naming_violations, begin_empty_mapping_document_value, attach_named_member_inside_mapping, add_number_to_object, emit_result_object_onto_standard_output.","module_name":"report-naming-policy-violations-record","package_name":"report-naming-policy-violations-record","function_definitions":{"report-naming-policy-violations-record":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"__argc","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"__argv","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_roots","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"roots"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_violations","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"violations"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_vcount","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"violation_count"},{"instruction_type":"varia